overview: Venu  is an orphan and a contractor at Vizag port. Anu is a student in classical singing. Sruthi  is Anu's friend. Anu makes an attempt to elope with her boyfriend Arun. Arun is the son of a Business tycoon JP. JP sends police across to nab Anu. As police nab Arun, Venu rescues Anu.
title: Nenunnanu
